{"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxpicker"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"platforms":[{"beta":false,"name":"iOS","introducedAt":"15.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false},{"beta":false,"name":"macOS","introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false},{"beta":false,"name":"visionOS","introducedAt":"1.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false}],"role":"symbol","title":"OUDSCheckboxPicker","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents18OUDSCheckboxPickerV","roleHeading":"Structure","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxPicker","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSCheckboxPicker","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"struct"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxPicker","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"A picker allowing to expose several checkboxes and select some of them within the others.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Each checkbox contains a “tag”, i.e. a supposed to be unique value.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The picker will expose the choosen values using this “tag”.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It has also some configuration elements which will override the one applied to nested ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","type":"reference"},{"text":" (divider, read only and error mode, layout and outlined)","type":"text"}],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxPicker\/init(selections:checkboxes:placement:isReversed:isError:isReadOnly:hasDivider:itemsSpacing:)"],"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers","generated":true},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxPicker\/body"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties","title":"Instance Properties","generated":true},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxPicker\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxPicker\/View-Implementations"],"anchor":"Default-Implementations","title":"Default Implementations","generated":true}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxPicker","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"Tag","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":"> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"where","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Tag","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Hashable","preciseIdentifier":"s:SH","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a chekcbox trait.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The picker itself does no have any defined accessiiblity value, label or identifier ; it remains in the users hands to define which one will be used.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However if defined in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioPickerData","isActive":true},{"text":" the items inside the picker will have such accessibility identifiers.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In addition the root item of the picker has for accessiiblity identifier the displayed text.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Forbidden by design","type":"heading","anchor":"Forbidden-by-design"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","isActive":true},{"text":" in both an error situation and a read only state.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The design system does not allow to have ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","isActive":true},{"text":" in both an error situation and a disabled state.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The design system does not allow to have ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","isActive":true},{"text":" in both a read only and a disabled state.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Code samples","type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Define the elements to display in checkboxes using OUDSCheckboxPickerData.","    \/\/ This object has the same properties as the OUDSCheckboxItem,","    \/\/ and some of them are optional with default values set","    var someDataToPopulate: [OUDSCheckboxPickerData<String>] {","        [","        OUDSCheckboxPickerData<String>(tag: \"Choice_1\",","                                       label: \"Virgin Holy Lava\",","                                       extraLabel: \"Very spicy\",","                                       helper: \"No alcohol, only tasty flavors\",","                                       icon: Image(systemName: \"flame\")),","","        OUDSCheckboxPickerData<String>(tag: \"Choice_2\",","                                       label: \"IPA beer\",","                                       helper: \"From Brewdog company\",","                                       icon: Image(systemName: \"dog.fill\")),","","        OUDSCheckboxPickerData<String>(tag: \"Choice_3\",","                                       label: \"Mineral water\",","                                       icon: Image(systemName: \"waterbottle.fill\")),","        ]","    }","","    \/\/ Prepare the selection, with a value previously selected","    \/\/ Use the data and the binding for the picker.","    @State var selections: [String] = [\"Choice_1\"] \/\/ or empty if nothing selected","","    \/\/ Here the picker is vertical by default","    OUDSCheckboxPicker(selections: $selections, checkboxes: someDataToPopulate)","","    \/\/ The picker can be vertical and have a root item with a label and a counter","    OUDSCheckboxPicker(selections: $selections,","                       placement: .verticalRooted(label, .textAndCount))","","    \/\/ The picker can apply some settings to all its radio buttons.","    \/\/ It can be also horizontal with a scroll indicator.","    \/\/ Here all the the checkboxes are in read only mode and use reversed layout.","    \/\/ Here the picker is horizontal and shows the scroll indicator","    OUDSCheckboxPicker(selections: $selections,","                       checkboxes: someDataToPopulate)","                       isReversed: true,","                       isReadOnly: true,","                       placement: .horizontal(true))"]},{"level":2,"text":"Design documentation","type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"There is no online specification as this component is not an official OUDS one","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Themes rendering","type":"heading","anchor":"Themes-rendering"},{"level":3,"text":"Orange","type":"heading","anchor":"Orange"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkboxPicker_Orange"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.14.0"}]}],"name":"Since","type":"aside","style":"note"}]}],"references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSCheckboxItem":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxitem","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItem"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItem"}],"title":"OUDSCheckboxItem","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Checkbox is a UI element that allows to select multiple options from a set of mutually non exclusive choices."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Checkbox item covers a wider range of contexts by allowing to toggle the visibility of additional text labels and icon assets.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSComponents/7SwiftUI4ViewP":{"type":"unresolvable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP","title":"SwiftUICore.View"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSCheckboxPicker/View-Implementations":{"role":"collectionGroup","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxpicker\/view-implementations","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxPicker\/View-Implementations","type":"topic","abstract":[],"kind":"article","title":"View Implementations"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentati